Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.05,0:00:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愛妳 愛到出神陶醉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.09,0:00:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愛妳 愛到懊惱萬分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.93,0:00:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼也不怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.40,0:00:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愛妳 無法忘記妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.58,0:00:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,風兒硬是拆開\N我們纏綿甜蜜的吻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.69,0:00:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,面對無法停止的熾熱心動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.96,0:00:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請不要流淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.76,0:00:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令人無法討厭的冷漠態度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.03,0:00:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,見不到面令我痛苦萬分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.90,0:01:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳鬱悶不樂的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.24,0:01:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令我心碎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.98,0:01:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愛妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.19,0:01:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愛妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.39,0:01:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愛妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.35,0:01:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.98,0:02:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天的菜色是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.55,0:02:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,炸蝦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.45,0:02:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請不要這樣,噁心死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.35,0:02:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.25,0:02:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是,請進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.76,0:02:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我菜做太多了\N方便的話,要不要拿去吃?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.53,0:02:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這真是謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.83,0:02:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.57,0:02:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你跟小津江約會回來的時候\N明明已經去她家大吃一頓了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.04,0:02:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.77,0:02:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說出來有什麼關係\N反正這是事實啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.91,0:02:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇,這個真的好香喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.88,0:02:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然你已經吃飽了\N那就沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.65,0:02:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四谷和朱美分著吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.68,0:02:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理…員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.25,0:02:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.52,0:03:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒喔,這是炸蝦唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.33,0:03:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.16,0:03:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你應該得下定決心\N讓自己痛苦得徹底一點比較好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.67,0:03:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是說啊\N你乾脆改追小津江好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.84,0:03:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用你們多管閒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.37,0:03:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小津江真的好可憐喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.58,0:03:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還以為自己有機會\N跟你這樣在耗時間…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.28,0:03:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,這個美味極了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.92,0:03:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#42五代骨折!戀愛的機會在病房!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.73,0:03:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,七次,這是新紀錄喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.97,0:03:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不會輸你呢,看我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.87,0:03:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好暖和喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.81,0:03:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好喜歡冬天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.01,0:03:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為可以吃烤地瓜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.72,0:03:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也是個原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.12,0:04:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏天熱到好像要融化似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.59,0:04:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冬天總讓人有一種緊張的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.72,0:04:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,一進了暖爐桌\N就什麼感覺都沒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.43,0:04:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.60,0:04:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比起夏天的冷氣\N我比較喜歡冬天的暖爐桌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.18,0:04:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以挽著你的手嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.38,0:04:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣靠在一起\N冬天的感覺也比夏天好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.39,0:04:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我臉上沾著地瓜嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.36,0:04:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有,只是覺得妳很可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.60,0:04:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭,討厭,討厭\N五代,你真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.42,0:05:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你回來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.59,0:05:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.03,0:05:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你跟小津江吵架了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.40,0:05:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你看起來沒什麼精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.07,0:05:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看起來會沒精神嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.40,0:05:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會吵架表示你們的感情很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.11,0:05:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不對?惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.98,0:05:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.92,0:05:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這還用問嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.22,0:05:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然是選擇被討厭囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.00,0:05:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想跟對方分手,又不想傷害對方\N只有這個辦法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.37,0:05:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以假裝自己是個變態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.04,0:06:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變態啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.91,0:06:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以前有演過戲嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.41,0:06:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.28,0:06:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過有時候會被同情\N反而會招來反效果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.65,0:06:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣,不如乾脆\N直接把缺點暴露出來比較…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.89,0:06:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比如說?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.56,0:06:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給她看你喝到爛醉的死樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.33,0:06:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者當著她的面\N和其他的女生親熱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.64,0:06:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平常你在管理員面前怎麼做\N照那樣做就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.47,0:06:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很簡單吧,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.61,0:06:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,小津江打電話找你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.82,0:06:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.66,0:06:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.77,0:07:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天?嗯,好啊\N我也有重要的事想跟妳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.78,0:07:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代說明天有重要的事\N要對小津江說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.65,0:07:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳又偷聽他講電話了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.02,0:07:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會是什麼事呢?\N說不定是要向她求婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.12,0:07:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好燙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.59,0:07:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.96,0:07:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他還只是個學生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.40,0:07:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼是要跟她分手嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.10,0:07:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道他們果真吵架了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.73,0:07:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果真?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.14,0:07:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天他和小津江約會回來之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.17,0:07:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就一付很沮喪的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.58,0:07:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還安慰他說\N吵架代表兩人感情很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.62,0:07:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,問題就在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.62,0:07:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳也真是罪孽深重啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.89,0:07:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,好燙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.30,0:08:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.07,0:08:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.64,0:08:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我房間的屋頂會漏水\N真的快受不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.74,0:08:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了,今天會修理好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.44,0:08:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.88,0:08:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.52,0:08:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好消沈喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.93,0:08:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,氣氛一旦變得很溫馨就完蛋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.73,0:08:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我今天要跟她談分手的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.81,0:08:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,這裡這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.43,0:09:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小津江,我跟妳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.46,0:09:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.03,0:09:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.47,0:09:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.64,0:09:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…請給我美式咖啡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.14,0:09:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.59,0:09:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡藍色嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.79,0:09:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?喜歡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.06,0:09:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.60,0:09:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你說喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.37,0:09:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來,這個送給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.93,0:09:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然聖誕節過了很久了\N穿穿看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.31,0:10:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不喜歡嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.55,0:10:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒那回事,謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.15,0:10:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎?我好高興喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.64,0:10:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烤地瓜,烤地瓜喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.89,0:10:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.30,0:10:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管…管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.93,0:10:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳…妳怎麼會在那裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.30,0:11:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在修理屋頂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.04,0:11:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,剛才你是不是\N罵了一聲“混蛋”?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.01,0:11:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.72,0:11:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請妳不要在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.18,0:11:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.55,0:11:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是四谷又欺負你了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.72,0:11:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.59,0:11:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.26,0:11:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可以算了\N我是這裡的管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.87,0:11:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以…所以算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.67,0:11:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.91,0:11:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種事我不能跟管理員說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.77,0:11:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟妳說也沒有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.48,0:11:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是跟響子說的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.21,0:11:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.46,0:11:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.74,0:12:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.19,0:13:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.86,0:13:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊!管…管理員!\N我馬上救妳下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.94,0:13:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了,反正我是個\N沒有管理能力的管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.84,0:13:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在胡說什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.21,0:13:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要緊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.34,0:13:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不會給房客添麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.08,0:13:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.13,0:13:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不叫我去救妳呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.74,0:13:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.54,0:13:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有什麼因為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.01,0:13:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那條排水管都快腐蝕掉了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.41,0:13:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.33,0:14:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我腳骨折之後的第三天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.85,0:14:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,在這裡在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.08,0:14:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨,你還好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.48,0:14:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓你久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.39,0:14:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來,這是管理員送的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.56,0:14:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她人呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.06,0:14:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月色皎潔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.43,0:14:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到包紮的膝蓋骨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.10,0:14:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的讓人覺得很心疼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.07,0:14:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她很難過喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.21,0:14:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她說都是她害你腳受傷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.28,0:15:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢,怎麼會說是她害我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.21,0:15:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.91,0:15:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然她很慌張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.25,0:15:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住院手續、準備換洗衣物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.92,0:15:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有連絡你家人的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.22,0:15:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她都幫你做得好好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.39,0:15:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.96,0:15:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,真討厭\N我都沒聽說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.79,0:15:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都不曉得你住院了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.23,0:15:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的腳怎麼會摔到骨折呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.43,0:15:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?為什麼?為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.00,0:15:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼啦,小津江…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.39,0:15:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.04,0:16:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.94,0:16:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代的情況怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.44,0:16:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳要是這麼擔心的話\N怎麼不自己去看他呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.92,0:16:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他看起來沒什麼精神喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.73,0:16:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,探病的蛋糕一口都沒吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.38,0:16:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員,妳就去看看他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.61,0:16:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在等妳去探病喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.04,0:17:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.91,0:17:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,等等啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.30,0:17:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等,我幹嘛偷偷摸摸躲起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.94,0:17:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我應該開朗一點…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.15,0:17:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.52,0:17:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明都已經走進來了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.46,0:18:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…真的很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.56,0:18:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要這麼說,是我自己不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.03,0:18:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳騙人的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.34,0:18:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼想都無所謂\N管理員好像準備照顧他到出院喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.84,0:18:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼…怎麼可能…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.92,0:18:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音無小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.85,0:18:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.85,0:18:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到妳我就放心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.09,0:18:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怕他假借照顧病人的名義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.92,0:18:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要求妳做這個做那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.92,0:18:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託妳做一大堆事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.06,0:18:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.20,0:18:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.56,0:18:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳的手除了幫他換衣服之外\N不能用來做其它的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.97,0:18:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.94,0:18:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果需要洗衣服請跟我說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.91,0:18:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會全部把它燒掉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.44,0:18:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.08,0:18:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.76,0:19:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看起來氣色不錯嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.53,0:19:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你現在來幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.39,0:19:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊\N你未免太過依賴音無小姐了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.53,0:19:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儘管她是管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.70,0:19:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是連住院都要讓她照顧\N這未免太離譜了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.44,0:19:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會這樣是有某些原因的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.78,0:19:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,你的意思是\N你是為了救她而骨折的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.88,0:19:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.32,0:19:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真可憐啊\N她這個人就是義務感太強了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.42,0:19:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,對喔,是因為義務感啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.32,0:19:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣,我懂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.96,0:19:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,今天我就先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.03,0:19:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,是因為義務感啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.26,0:19:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是因為義務感呢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.52,0:20:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳好認真喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.15,0:20:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像已經超越了\N管理員跟房客的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.42,0:20:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪有,才沒有那回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.55,0:20:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有那回事呢,我只是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.89,0:20:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為照顧他是我的義務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.69,0:21:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天氣好好喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.32,0:21:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思\N這麼好的天氣還要來照顧我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.42,0:21:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.53,0:21:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要去庭院走走?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.40,0:21:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.00,0:21:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會不會冷?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.47,0:21:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊的,今天好安靜喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.31,0:21:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.48,0:21:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳放著一刻館跑來這不要緊嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.95,0:21:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不用擔心那種事情\N更何況…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.19,0:21:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更何況什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.59,0:21:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更何況…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.57,0:22:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.71,0:22:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好美喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.51,0:22:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危險!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.36,0:23:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.06,0:23:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好…好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.31,0:23:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,滑雪時摔到腳骨折了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.31,0:23:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真丟臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.42,0:23:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以特地來這間醫院住院?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.42,0:23:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還指定這間病房嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.42,0:23:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係,我會每天來看你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.53,0:23:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這像是帥哥會做的事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.84,0:23:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這個人好像沒什麼信用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.28,0:23:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我的確是因為音無小姐在\N才來這家醫院住院的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.78,0:23:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.52,0:24:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「戀愛的火花衝擊\N五代和三鷹住院騷動」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.42,0:24:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代\N看來不好好跟你說清楚是不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.57,0:24:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當我們互相凝視時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.80,0:24:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會有一道奇妙的旋律\N在心中迴響著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.88,0:24:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無法用言語來表達愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:40.59,0:24:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只好彈奏起了鋼琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:47.13,0:24:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請把夢丟進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.47,0:24:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為我測量一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:54.20,0:24:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛有多深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:59.04,0:25:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用輕觸的嘴唇演奏著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:05.28,0:25:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平靜的合聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:12.22,0:25:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使擁抱著妳依然惆悵滿懷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:18.43,0:25:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夢見了Fantasy
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:25.50,0:25:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開啟了只有我們兩人\N才看得見的門扉Fantasy
